fullDescription.markdown: Ensure all properties are unique for a given location using a unique combination of @ns, @name, @class. @group. and @value.
Ensure all links are unique for a given location using a unique combination of @href, @rel, and @media-type.
A local reference SHOULD NOT have a media-type.
A `title` is required when a `citation` is provided.
A resource should provide at least an `rlink` or `base64` object.
Ensure that each rlink item references a unique resource.
